Ubuntu-22.04-x64 run go app

1. 安装图形化桌面

ssh root@100.10.10.100 "apt-get update && apt-get install -y ubuntu-desktop"

2
ssh root@100.10.10.100 "apt-get install -y xrdp && systemctl enable xrdp && systemctl start xrdp"

3
ssh root@100.10.10.100 "apt-get install -y gnome-session gdm3 && systemctl enable gdm3 && systemctl start gdm3"

4 检查服务状态：
ssh root@100.10.10.100 "systemctl status gdm3 && systemctl status xrdp"

5.


1
/*
$env:GOOS="linux"; $env:GOARCH="amd64"; go build -o go_server_linux
*/

2 upload
scp go_server_linux root@100.10.88.999:/root/
